						<summary>

						<p>The inscription is much damaged. It seems to record an endowment of land after purchase, for the requirements of worship in the temple of Tiruvoṟṟiyūr-Mahādēva by <hi rend="bold">Nambaṉ Dīraṉ a native of Maṅgalam</hi> on the northern bank of the Veṇṇāṟu river <hi rend="bold">in Śōḻa-[nāḍu].</hi> This might be a record of Parāntaka I.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
